Description: TMJOs system identity (/etc/os-release, lsb-release, issue)
 Replaces the Debian identity files with TMJOs-branded versions:
  * /etc/os-release    — TMJOs 2.0 alpha on Debian 13 trixie, shown in
                         GNOME About and tools that read PRETTY_NAME / ID
  * /etc/lsb-release   — TMJOs 2.0 alpha, codename trixie, for legacy
                         scripts that still read lsb_release output
  * /etc/issue         — "TMJOs <ver> \n \l" banner shown at TTY login
